structure.unit: TRAFFIC REGULATIONS -- VEHICLE EQUIPMENT AND STORAGE

law.history: Repealed 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 48, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 126, sec. 24. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 8, secs. 1 and 2.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Permit required for installation of television set in motor vehicle.
